==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unriddle
<hw>Un*rid"dle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>riddle</ets>.]</ety> <def>To read the riddle of;
to solve or explain; <as>as, to <ex>unriddle</ex> an enigma or a
mystery</as>.</def> <rj><au>Macaulay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And where you can't <qex>unriddle</qex>, learn to trust.</q>
<rj><qau>Parnell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unriddler</ent>⟦br⟧
